Hey, hey, Doc, where are you? Thank god I found you. Listen, can you meet me at Twin Pines Mall
tonight at 1:15? I've made a major breakthrough, I'll need your assistance. Wait a minute, wait a
minute. 1:15 in the morning? Yeah. What's going on? Where have you been all week?(Marty hides
in the back of the car.) (v.o) Don't forget to turn off the garage lights! (Biff gets in his car and drives
off. As he leaves the Tannen house, Doc rides past on a bicycle. Doc rides up the driveway to the
empty garage and rings the bell.) Marty, Marty! Marty!
Looking down again, Marty jumps off the roof. Biff looks at him with a "what the hell?" look and ap
proaches the roof. He chuckles to himself. Then he sees Marty hovering in mid-air! It turns out that
he's standing on the DeLorean. What the hell?
